---
import DocsLayout from '../../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
---

<DocsLayout
	title="Need help?"
	description="Get support for GetCookie. Find resources and contact our team."
>
	<h1>Need Help?</h1>
	<p class="lead">
		Stuck on something? We're happy to help you get the most out of GetCookie!
	</p>

	<h2>Common Issues</h2>

	<div class="accordion">
		<details class="accordion-item">
			<summary>GetCookie is not responding</summary>
			<div class="accordion-content">
				<p>If GetCookie isn't responding to commands, try the following:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Make sure the bot has the required permissions in your server</li>
					<li>Check if the bot is online in the member list</li>
					<li>Ensure you're in a channel where the bot has access</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</details>

		<details class="accordion-item">
			<summary>Cannot give or receive Cookies</summary>
			<div class="accordion-content">
				<p>If you're having trouble giving Cookies:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Make sure you have Cookies to give (check your balance)</li>
					<li>Verify you're tagging a valid server member</li>
					<li>Check if there are any server-specific restrictions set by admins</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</details>

		<details class="accordion-item">
			<summary>Leaderboard not updating</summary>
			<div class="accordion-content">
				<p>If the leaderboard seems stuck:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Leaderboards updates periodically — wait a few minutes</li>
					<li>Try the command again to force a refresh</li>
					<li>Clear Discord's cache by restarting the app</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</details>

	</div>

	<h2>Contact Us</h2>
	<p>
		For other inquiries, you can reach us through:
	</p>
